channel.title: [fixed] problem with login
channel.description:
well heres the fuking problem
i have a server , i run project 16 v4 and its fine i have run my server lots of times with people on it i just ran it yesterday
but today its not working !!!! i did not changed any computer settings nothing i was playing runescape so i dont know what this can be.
Note: i already tried testscape source i have here and it didnt worked so it isnt source problem.
and yes im using the defaut port and i have it added in exceptions tab.
thx for the help. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
the problem was simple i had to make a new server ip. now its working. if u have the same problem i had i hope this helps.
